border-color:initial;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;outline:0px;max-width:100%;border-width:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:initial;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"65\" data-ratio=\"0.11296296296296296\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:578px;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:center;height:auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=be35e013&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fg0kpxARkI2QPgPA868wyn0LFMFlv18uosEWwB4iaKPdBBHJlD4GYRHOytPia6moa4MPQDibjKXtvUvts27RcWa5OQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></span></p>\n  <ne-clipboard source=\"https%3A%2F%2Fwww.yuque.com%2Fqone%2Fyys%2Ffernr4qrl16tfb2z%2Fedit%3Ftoc_node_uuid%3DXhFjaOJFod2FRcI4%23YHgv6\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"></ne-clipboard>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;text-align:left;\"><span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px;\">▌AI 聊天界面需新设计，优化信息展示和用户体验</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://lukew.com/ff/entry.asp?2135\" target=\"_blank\">https://lukew.com/ff/entry.asp?2135</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"white-space: normal;line-height: 2em;margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;text-align: left;\"><span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">本文提出一种用于带有工具调用和思维过程的代理式聊天 UI 的改进思路：将“过程信息”（思维轨迹、工具调用）与“结果”分离，设计成双滚动面板的布局，使用户在一个列查看指令与思维过程，在另一个列查看最终结果，初始指令及过程在左列汇总，结果在右列持续可滚动显示。通过这种分离与并行展示，既保留对模型内部过程的可理解性，又避免在窄屏/侧边栏场景中产生大量滚动与信息混乱，提升上下文保持与对话协作的效率。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"501968358\" data-type=\"png\" width=\"1606\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-w=\"1080\" data-ratio=\"0.5824074074074074\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=54bea0b8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fg0kpxARkI2StHiaH2icCibzvZ3KIpBiaGfCsGrrWAWC6iaXvlfibaiawKGwg60789Oqt88cic8nruFR6BXFQMm9nV2FVcg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;text-align:left;\"><span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px;\">▌AI 智能体如何利用文件系统进行上下文工程</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://baoyu.io/translations/how-agents-can-use-filesystems-for-context-engineering\" target=\"_blank\">https://baoyu.io/translations/how-agents-can-use-filesystems-for-context-engineering</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"white-space: normal;line-height: 2em;margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;text-align: left;\"><span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">本文阐述了文件系统在AI智能体中的关键作用，强调通过统一的文件系统接口，智能体可以更高效地存储、检索和更新上下文，从而避免因上下文不足、上下文过载或信息检索不当而导致的“翻车”现象，并通过示例与方法论展示如何将大规模上下文管理转化为可控的草稿纸式存储与智能化检索。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"501968357\" data-type=\"png\" width=\"589\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-w=\"589\" data-ratio=\"0.567062818336163\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a071d24a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fg0kpxARkI2StHiaH2icCibzvZ3KIpBiaGfCsZvVejGYosgWXnNUWPE1JiaOQr2WB9iarWHHZPTeYrCic6JxrXAibqJuLUQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <div>\n   <h2 data-node-type=\"block\" data-block-type=\"text\" style=\"margin: 24px 8px;white-space: normal;line-height: 2em;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 48px 8px 24px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"65\" data-ratio=\"0.11296296296296296\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 578px;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c6cd7e58&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fg0kpxARkI2QPgPA868wyn0LFMFlv18uoVw3ibDBtUOIklnu30LHYQBArbGTZwnwokZzibw3DIeVlsscsP5PcbC3A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></span></p>\n    <ne-clipboard source=\"https%3A%2F%2Fwww.yuque.com%2Fqone%2Fyys%2Ffernr4qrl16tfb2z%2Fedit%3Ftoc_node_uuid%3DXhFjaOJFod2FRcI4%23YHgv6\" data-pm-s